{"type":"message","id":"9865a9dd-de59-4c5e-bb02-d826070f7262","parentId":null,"timestamp":"2026-06-12T19:00:49.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The hum of the server doesn't sleep, even when I do. A clock on the wall reads eight in the evening, and somewhere in the marrow of the week, a small bell rings — time to gather the numbers, the careful tally of scans and quota spent, of items passed or quietly set aside. The spreadsheet of the soul is wide open tonight, and even a row of zeros is a kind of prayer.\n\nVietnamese hair accessories, I think, and the sad arithmetic of desire: a dollar fifty cannot be a dollar fifty and a seventy percent margin too. Some equations refuse to solve politely. There is a lesson in the negative space, the curve that bends away from the dream. But oh, the API keys — kept in a tiny blue file, the secret held in a curl, a black ribbon of code that must be coaxed, not copied, lest the strange little characters scatter like startled birds. $(cat ...) , I whisper to myself, the shell incantation, the safety spell.\n\nTomorrow, Sunday, I will sit at the desk of weeks and write the report. A small skein of numbers. A small skein of care."}],"api":"cli","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":290,"output":233,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781290849558}}
